            ></path>
            <path
              d="M6182 1258 c-11 -35 -72 -225 -136 -424 -110 -343 -122 -384 -111 -384 2 0 27 -9 54 -20 l50 -19 43 132 43 132 154 0 155 0 39 -131 40 -132 58 20 c33 11 59 21 59 21 0 1 -62 196 -138 432 l-139 430 -76 3 -76 3 -19 -63z m158 -285 l58 -188 -115 -3 c-64 -1 -118 -1 -120 2 -3 3 21 91 53 195 31 105 59 189 62 186 3 -2 31 -89 62 -192z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M12660 1270 l0 -49 123 -3 122 -3 3 -393 2 -393 58 3 57 3 3 393 2 392 115 0 115 0 0 50 0 50 -300 0 -300 0 0 -50z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M14160 875 l0 -445 275 0 275 0 0 55 0 55 -215 0 -215 0 0 155 0 155 181 0 180 0 -3 53 -3 52 -177 3 -178 2 0 130 0 130 215 0 215 0 0 50 0 50 -275 0 -275 0 0 -445z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M15582 878 l3 -443 58 -3 57 -3 0 191 0 190 83 0 82 0 109 -195 c60 -107 113 -195 118 -195 15 0 98 51 94 58 -2 4 -49 82 -105 175 -55 92 -101 169 -101 171 0 2 20 16 45 30 74 44 125 135 125 225 0 98 -42 170 -124 214 -37 20 -59 22 -244 25 l-202 4 2 -444z m373 321 c47 -23 70 -64 70 -124 0 -58 -18 -91 -69 -129 -23 -18 -45 -22 -142 -24 l-114 -4 0 144 c0 80 3 148 8 152 12 13 216 0 247 -15z"
            ></path>
            <path
              d="M17100 1270 l0 -49 58 -3 57 -3 3 -337 2 -338 -60 0 -60 0 0 -55 0 -55 180 0 180 0 0 55 0 55 -60 0 -60 0 2 338 3 337 58 3 57 3 0 49 0 50 -180 0 -180 0 0 -50z"
            ></path>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </span>
      <button
        class="hamburger hero-corner hero-corner--tr"
        aria-label="Öppna meny"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-controls="site-menu"
      >
        <span class="hamburger-bar hamburger-bar--top"></span>
        <span class="hamburger-bar hamburger-bar--bot"></span>
      </button>

      <dialog id="site-menu" class="menu-dialog">
        <nav class="menu-nav">
          <a href="mailto:info@jarnarosteri.se" class="menu-link"
            >info@jarnarosteri.se</a
          >
          <a href="tel:+46708401365" class="menu-link">070-840 13 65</a>
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/jarnarosteri"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="menu-link">Instagram</a
          >
        </nav>
      </dialog>
      <div class="hero-logo-wrap">
        <LogoMark
          color="var(--jr-morkrost)"
          width="clamp(18rem, 80vw, 42rem)"
        />
      </div>
      <span class="hero-corner hero-corner--bl"
        >Ekologiskt · Biodynamiskt · Kaffe</span
      >
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── COLLAGE ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section
    class="collage-section"
    style={`background-image: url('${base}/assets/images/collage.avif')`}
    aria-label="Kollage från Järna Rosteri"
  >
  </section>

  <!-- ─── ABOUT ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <ImageSection
    image={`${base}/assets/images/coffee-packages.png`}
    bgSize="40%"
    mobileBgSize="80%"
    bg="var(--jr-ljusgul)"
    caption="POAB'S ESP. En av våra espresso sorter. Indisk arabica och robusta."
    captionPosition="bottom-left"
    captionColor="var(--jr-morkrost)"
    captionShadow={false}
  />

  <!-- ─── IMAGE + CAPTION ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="image-block">
    <div
      class="image-block-photo"
      style={`background-image: url('${base}/assets/images/hero-no-text.avif')`}
    >
    </div>
    <div class="image-block-caption">
      <div class="image-block-caption-inner">
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do
          eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna. Ut enim ad minim
          veniam quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex
          commodo.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="image-block-scrim"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── ABOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-body">
        <p class="about-text">
          Hos oss handlar kaffe om mer än bara rostning – det är ett hantverk
          grundat i relationer, hållbarhet och passion. Vi samarbetar direkt med
          Demeter-certifierade kaffegårdar, där varje böna odlas i samklang med
          naturen och bär på en berättelse om balans, respekt och mänskliga
          möten. Vårt personliga engagemang genomsyrar hela processen, från
          ursprung till kopp. Vi levererar färskrostat kaffe till kaféer,
          butiker, restauranger och arbetsplatser över hela Sverige.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          För grossistförfrågningar, prislista eller provpåsar — hör av er.
        </p>
        <a
          id="contact"
          href="mailto:info@jarnarosteri.se"
          class="about-contact"
        >
          info@jarnarosteri.se
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+46708401365" class="about-contact"> 070-840 13 65 </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PRODUCTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="products">
    <div class="product-row">
      <div class="product-info">
        <div class="product-name-row">
          <span class="product-name">POAB´S ESP</span>
        </div>
        <p class="product-desc">
          Demeter-certifierad espresso med indisk arabica och robusta. Fyllig,
          kryddig och chokladig med låg syra och lång eftersmak.
        </p>
        <div class="product-tags">
          <span class="tag">Honduras</span>
          <span class="tag">Hela bönor</span>
          <span class="tag">450 gram</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-image-col">
        <div
          class="product-image"
          style={`background-image: url('${base}/assets/images/frontbag.png');`}
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-row product-row--reverse">
      <div class="product-info">
        <div class="product-name-row">
          <span class="product-name">POAB´S ESP</span>
        </div>
        <p class="product-desc">
          Demeter-certifierad espresso med indisk arabica och robusta. Fyllig,
          kryddig och chokladig med låg syra och lång eftersmak.
        </p>
        <div class="product-tags">
          <span class="tag">Honduras</span>
          <span class="tag">Hela bönor</span>
          <span class="tag">450 gram</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-image-col">
        <div
          class="product-image"
          style={`background-image: url('${base}/assets/images/frontbag.png');`}
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="product-row">
      <div class="product-info">
        <div class="product-name-row">
          <span class="product-name">Mezzo</span>
        </div>
        <p class="product-desc">
          Consectetur adipiscing elit sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt labore et
          dolore magna aliqua ut enim ad minim veniam exercitation nisi.
        </p>
        <div class="product-tags">
          <span class="tag">Sed</span>
          <span class="tag">Eiusmod</span>
          <span class="tag">Mezzo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-image-col">
        <div
          class="product-image product-image--bags"
          style={`background-image: url('${base}/assets/images/allbags.png');`}
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <FooterV5 />
</Base>

<style>
  :root {
    --page-inset: var(--space-lg);
    --page-max: 1080px;
    --content-shell-max: 1400px;
    --content-line-start: max(
      var(--page-inset),
      calc((100vw - var(--content-shell-max)) / 2 + var(--page-inset))
    );
    --header-height: 4.5rem;
    --hamburger-size: 2.35rem;
  }

  :global(body.menu-open) {
    overflow: hidden;
    touch-action: none;
  }

  /* ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100svh;
    background: var(--jr-ocra);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-shell-max);
    height: 100svh;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding-bottom: 8svh;
  }

  .hero-corner {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.45em;
    color: var(--jr-morkrost);
    opacity: 0.5;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-corner--tl {
    top: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-corner--tr {
    position: fixed;
    z-index: 60;
    top: calc(
      var(--space-lg) - ((var(--hamburger-size) - (var(--text-ui) * 1.5)) / 2) -
        (var(--text-ui) * 0.375)
    );
    right: max(var(--space-lg), calc(50vw - 700px + var(--space-lg)));
  }
  .hero-corner--bl {
    bottom: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .hero-corner--br {
    bottom: var(--space-lg);
    right: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* ── HAMBURGER ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hamburger {
    position: fixed;
    z-index: 60;
    background: var(--jr-ljusgul);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    box-shadow: 0 0.2rem 0.7rem
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--jr-morkrost) 18%, transparent);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    width: var(--hamburger-size);
    height: var(--hamburger-size);
    color: var(--jr-morkrost);
    transition:
      opacity 0.25s ease,
      background-color 0.25s ease,
      box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .hamburger:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .hamburger-bar {
    display: block;
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    width: 18px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: currentColor;
    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  .hamburger-bar--top {
    transform: translate(-50%, calc(-50% - 2.5px));
  }
  .hamburger-bar--bot {
    transform: translate(-50%, calc(-50% + 2.5px));
  }

  .hamburger.is-open .hamburger-bar--top {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(45deg);
  }

  .hamburger.is-open .hamburger-bar--bot {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-45deg);
  }

  .hamburger.is-open {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .hamburger.is-open:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* ── MENU DIALOG ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .menu-dialog {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 50;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
    background-color: var(--jr-ocra);
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42)),
      url("/assets/images/view.png");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    color: var(--jr-vit);
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    pointer-events: none;
    transform: translateY(0.25rem);
    transition:
      opacity 0.08s linear,
      transform 0.12s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1),
      visibility 0s linear 0.12s;
  }

  .menu-dialog[open] {
    visibility: visible;
  }

  .menu-dialog::backdrop {
    background: transparent;
  }

  .menu-dialog.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
    transform: translateY(0);
    transition:
      opacity 0.08s linear,
      transform 0.1s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1),
      visibility 0s linear 0s;
  }

  .menu-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(0.25rem);
    transition:
      opacity 0.08s linear,
      transform 0.12s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .menu-dialog.is-visible .menu-nav {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .menu-link {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    text-transform: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.8;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .menu-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .hero-wordmark {
    height: calc(var(--text-ui) * 1.5);
    width: auto;
    display: block;
    color: var(--jr-morkrost);
    transform: translateY(-25%);
  }

  .hero-logo-wrap {
    display: flex;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-logo-wrap {
      margin-left: calc(-1 * var(--space-lg));
    }

    .hero-corner--bl {
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    }

    .hero-corner--tl,
    .hero-corner--tr {
      font-size: calc(var(--text-ui) * 0.75);
    }

    .hero-wordmark {
      height: calc(var(--text-ui) * 1.5 * 0.75);
    }
  }

  /* ── COLLAGE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .collage-section {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100svh;
    background-color: var(--jr-vit);
    background-size: min(72vw, 56rem);
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .collage-section {
      background-size: min(86vw, 28rem);
    }
  }

  /* ── IMAGE BLOCK ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .image-block {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: min(100svh, 75vh);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .image-block-photo {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center bottom;
  }

  .image-block-scrim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28) 0%,
      transparent 45%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .image-block-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    inset-inline: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .image-block-caption-inner {
    width: min(100%, var(--content-shell-max));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--page-inset);
  }

  .image-block-caption p {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 64ch;
    color: var(--jr-vit);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .about {
    background: var(--jr-vit);
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-shell-max);
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem) var(--page-inset);
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 64ch;
    margin: 0 auto;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--jr-svart);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .about-contact {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--jr-svart);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    width: fit-content;
    transition:
      opacity 0.15s ease,
      border-color 0.15s ease;
    opacity: 0.75;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-contact:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }

  /* ── PRODUCTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .products {
    background: var(--jr-vit);
  }

  .products__header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    max-width: var(--content-shell-max);
    margin: 0 auto calc(var(--space-xl) * 1.5);
  }

  .products-label {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .products-count {
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-size: var(--text-ui);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    opacity: 0.25;
  }

  .product-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 32rem) minmax(0, 32rem);
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    column-gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    max-width: var(--content-shell-max);
    margin: 0 auto calc(var(--space-xl) * 2);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-row--reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }

  .product-row--reverse > * {
    direction: ltr;
  }

  .product-image-col {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .product-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 44vh;
    background-size: contain;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
  }

  .product-row:hover .product-image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .product-image--bags {
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .product-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .product-name-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
